high_descs: Head towards the black fridge and then hang a left and cross the room to the white table.
Pick up the egg that is sitting on the table to the right of the loaf of bread
Turn around and head to the sink on your left

Place the egg in the sink to the very left; Place it the the left of the left hand spatula then turn on the faucet and fill the sink with water. Turn of the faucet then pick up the egg that is on the very left hand side of the sink
Head to the white table on your left then turn right to face the black shelf
Place the egg on the top shelf to the right of the egg that is already on the table
anns.task_desc: Place a clean egg on a shelf

high_descs: Turn left and go to the white table.
Pick up the egg on the table.
Turn around, go to the sink, face the sink on the left.
Wash the egg in the sink with water.
Take the egg to the small black table, left of the sink.
Put the egg on the small black table.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned egg on the small black table.

high_descs: Walk forward two steps, then turn left and walk across the room.
Pick up the egg on the white table.
Turn around and take two steps, then turn left to face the sink.
Place the egg in the left side of the sink, beside the spatula. Turn on the faucet for two seconds, then turn off the faucet and pick up the egg.
Turn to the left and walk across the room, then turn to the right.
Place the egg on the right side of the table, next to the other egg.
